import React from "react"
import { Row, Col, Image, Header, Footer, Sider, Content } from 'antd';

const Profile = () => {
  return (

      <Header>Header</Header>
      <Layout>

    <Layout>

      <Layout>
        <Content>Content</Content>
        <Sider>Sider</Sider>
      </Layout>

      <Sider>Sider</Sider>
      <Layout>
        <Header>Header</Header>
        <Content>Content</Content>
        <Footer>Footer</Footer>
      </Layout>
    </Layout>
  
      <Col span={20}>
        <Image
          width={1000}
          src="http://localhost:3000/HR_employee.png"
        />
      </Col>
    </Row>
  );
};

export default Profile;
